      "content": "hey so i had the weirdest thing happen today. i was at the cafe in downtown and saw this guy in a red jacket, totally unremarkable. then like twenty mins later i'm walking near the park and i see the exact same guy, same jacket, same way he was holding his phone. it felt... i dont know, like a lag or something? has this ever happened to u or am i just losing it?",
